trans-unit.source: Contains identification and initialization information about a <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> object.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> 개체에 대한 ID 및 초기화 정보를 포함합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the unique identifier for the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />.
The unique identifier for the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />.
Gets a value that indicates whether the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> has been initialized.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />가 초기화되었는지 여부를 나타내는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> has been initialized; otherwise <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />가 초기화되었으면 <see langword="true" />이고, 그렇지 않으면 <see langword="false" />입니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value that uniquely identifies the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> when the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> is in an uninitialized state.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />가 초기화되지 않은 상태인 경우 <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />를 고유하게 식별하는 값을 가져옵니다.

trans-unit.source: A value that uniquely identifies the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> when the <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" /> is in an uninitialized state.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />가 초기화되지 않은 상태인 경우 <see cref="T:System.Activities.BookmarkScope" />를 고유하게 식별하는 값입니다.

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Activities.BookmarkScope> is initialized, the returned value is `null`.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.Activities.BookmarkScope> 은 반환 된 값이 초기화 `null`합니다.
